data.description: ***Assumable FHA loan on this home with great rate****This gorgeous brick house with a huge lot in Athmar Park is the perfect place to call home! The atmosphere is warm and inviting and features real wood flooring, central heat/air, a huge fenced yard, and great outdoor space to relax on gorgeous Colorado evenings.  The home is a wonderfully affordable option with no HOA and a large two car garage.  There is also plenty of room for extra vehicles/RV(s) if you need the space.  Upgrades have been made to the water heater, the furnace, and the air conditioner.   Athmar Park is in an amazing central location.  It is just 20 minutes to Red Rocks and 15 minutes to Downtown Denver.  Come make this beautiful brick bungalow your very own!
